Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.77,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, a story where we both escape our deaths would've been nice as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:51.65,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Something like in {\i1}Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid{\i0} or {\i1}Bonnie and Clyde{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:55.91,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Or a story where we both fight a common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:00.37,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,But the strong point here is the battle of two comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.16,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Maybe a battle for our homeland? For our families?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.91,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Something like {\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.42,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,A setting like that would be a bit too predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:12.09,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,We could have you kill Yuuta by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:18.47,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,So Dark Flame Master gets the deathly role of someone like {\i1}Mercutio{\i0} or {\i1}Tybalt{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.85,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't that be a bit far-fetched as our setting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.35,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,It's enjoyable precisely because situations like that can't actually happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:26.94,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:32.53,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,I really wouldn't want to come to hate him just because he's playing our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:41.70,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,No, no, that wasn't supposed to mean I like him or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:42.79,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:49.92,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Dark Flame Master ignores his contract with me and falls in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.42,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,You're talking about our setting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.68,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,Driven by anger I have to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.89,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,And that's when the Dark Flame Master Robot, controlled by Yuuta, enters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.43,Defaultchu2,,0,0,0,,to fight me!
